Description: Python Monero module
        ====================
        
        |travis|_ |coveralls|_
        
        
        .. |travis| image:: https://travis-ci.org/monero-ecosystem/monero-python.svg
        .. _travis: https://travis-ci.org/monero-ecosystem/monero-python
        
        
